---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Offline - EnergieVergleich NRW"
  description="Sie sind aktuell offline. Bitte überprüfen Sie Ihre Internetverbindung."
>
  <div class="offline-container">
    <div class="offline-content">
      <div class="offline-icon">
        <svg
          width="120"
          height="120"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="1.5"
        >
          <path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"></path>
          <polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"></polyline>
          <line x1="1" y1="1" x2="23" y2="23" stroke="#ef4444" stroke-width="2"></line>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <h1 class="offline-title">Sie sind offline</h1>

      <p class="offline-description">
        Es scheint, als hätten Sie keine aktive Internetverbindung. Bitte überprüfen Sie Ihre
        Verbindung und versuchen Sie es erneut.
      </p>

      <div class="offline-actions">
        <button onclick="window.location.reload()" class="btn btn-primary"> 🔄 Neu laden </button>
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-secondary"> 🏠 Zur Startseite </a>
      </div>

      <div class="offline-tips">
        <h2>Tipps zur Fehlerbehebung:</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Überprüfen Sie Ihre WLAN-Verbindung</li>
          <li>Stellen Sie sicher, dass der Flugmodus deaktiviert ist</li>
          <li>Versuchen Sie, den Router neu zu starten</li>
          <li>Warten Sie einen Moment und versuchen Sie es erneut</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="cached-pages">
        <h3>Verfügbare Offline-Inhalte:</h3>
        <p>Einige Seiten wurden für die Offline-Nutzung gespeichert:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/">Startseite</a></li>
          <li><a href="/stromvergleich-nrw">Stromvergleich</a></li>
          <li><a href="/gasvergleich-nrw">Gasvergleich</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .offline-container {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f8fafc, #ffffff);
  }

  .offline-content {
    max-width: 600px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .offline-icon {
    color: #64748b;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .offline-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #1e293b;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .offline-description {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: #475569;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .offline-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn {
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: #2563eb;
    color: white;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: #1d4ed8;
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: white;
    color: #2563eb;
    border: 2px solid #2563eb;
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: #eff6ff;
  }

  .offline-tips {
    background: #eff6ff;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .offline-tips h2 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1e293b;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .offline-tips ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .offline-tips li {
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    color: #475569;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .offline-tips li::before {
    content: '✓';
    display: inline-block;
    width: 1.5rem;
    height: 1.5rem;
    background: #2563eb;
    color: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
    margin-right: 0.75rem;
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .cached-pages {
    background: #f8fafc;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .cached-pages h3 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1e293b;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .cached-pages p {
    color: #64748b;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cached-pages ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .cached-pages li {
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
  }

  .cached-pages a {
    color: #2563eb;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .cached-pages a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
